{"tid":860304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★警務處今（13日）舉行秋季招募日，吸引大批應徵者。","createTime":"2018-10-13T08:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T09:16:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"024e08c73515e4351f328214b5902875951e37c9","tid":860304,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1968114/org/8ec69fcb8d03fc7bd3e0c048045c6e44.JPG/CwrPEthKO3n-nhFmSjrTcgLbYY2znKNYC_SZbAv0mWw?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1968114%2Forg%2F8ec69fcb8d03fc7bd3e0c048045c6e44.JPG%2FCwrPEthKO3n-nhFmSjrTcgLbYY2znKNYC_SZbAv0mWw%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=f34a5ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方今舉行秋季招募日，吸引大批大專畢業生投考。剛在香港大學幼兒教育系畢業的張小姐，就希望可以加入警隊的保護兒童組。她表示過去曾經參與制服隊伍，發現自己對幫助市民有熱誠，並且曾參加警隊學長計劃，對督察的工作感到興趣，因而前來投考見習督察一職。<br />\n<br />\n張小姐認為，朱經緯案件是個別事件，「相信仲<span style=\"color: red;\">有99%督察、警察都做得非常好</span>，我非常欣賞。」她又提到，若通過遴選將有9個月的督察訓練，而且警隊有內部守則，有信心可面對及化解衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1968104/org/92ce7bbbff2746e2ec1279f7b0de5f44.JPG/Uwyt1ySQfYrTp-dVbsopUIHb4VIY42fl_vMfqf7zH6k?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1968104%2Forg%2F92ce7bbbff2746e2ec1279f7b0de5f44.JPG%2FUwyt1ySQfYrTp-dVbsopUIHb4VIY42fl_vMfqf7zH6k%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=0381cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/246578/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%8B%9B%E5%8B%9F%E6%97%A5-%E6%8A%95%E8%80%83%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E6%A1%88%E5%B1%AC%E5%80%8B%E5%88%A5%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-99-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%BE%97%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E5%A5%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F246578%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%258B%259F%25E6%2597%25A5-%2